Source: fortishield-indexer
Section: web
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Fortishield Indexer Team <info@fortishield.github.io>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://www.fortishield.github.io/

Package: fortishield-indexer
Architecture: any
Description: Fortishield indexer is a near real-time full-text search and analytics engine that gathers security-related data into one platform.
 This Fortishield central component indexes and stores alerts generated by the Fortishield server.
 Fortishield indexer can be configured as a single-node or multi-node cluster, providing scalability and high availability.
 Documentation can be found at https://documentation.fortishield.github.io/current/getting-started/components/fortishield-indexer.html

